<includeonly>{{#invoke:RecipeTable|main|id={{{1|{{{id|}}}}}}|mode={{{mode|producing}}}}}</includeonly><noinclude>
{{doc}}
Renders a recipe table for an item or element.

'''Usage:'''
* <code><nowiki>{{RecipeTable|IronIngot}}</nowiki></code> — recipes that produce Iron Ingot
* <code><nowiki>{{RecipeTable|IronIngot|mode=consuming}}</nowiki></code> — recipes that consume Iron Ingot
* <code><nowiki>{{RecipeTable|IronIngot|mode=all}}</nowiki></code> — all recipes involving Iron Ingot

'''Parameters:'''
* '''1''' (or '''id'''): Item or element template identifier (required)
* '''mode''': <code>producing</code> (default), <code>consuming</code>, or <code>all</code>

[[Category:Data templates]]
</noinclude>
